      Editor of a commentary on  Statius' Thebais, probably active in Rome. The core of this work comprises a mass of  Scholia - 
      conceived more as a commentary on subject and style (geography, mythology, rhetoric) than as a glossary - which, if used by Servius [5. 153ff.], probably 
